Vercheck allows to make several actions on users according to their version
{command} [add/del/set/show/list] [name/os] [kick/ban/visitor/filter] <name or os>
*/{command} list
Bot will show the list of version rules for this room
*/{command} add name ban Talkonaut
Bot will ban everyone who has Talkonaut in their version name.
*/{command} del name Talkonaut ban
Bot will remove the rule that matches name Talkonaut and action ban